{"tid":84594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（集體回憶） 有冇人細個食過一隻西瓜雪條","createTime":"2017-01-17T15:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T16:20:57.000Z","uid":30208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aee749bbd76a64cb2f9794b9a07be68935cf6584","tid":84594,"uid":30208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"細個食過一隻西瓜雪條， 個形狀係一片三角形既西瓜， 然後上面既黑色核係朱古力碎黎，有冇人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我揾唔到圖， 條囡話我吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a41aaad515839587f0483a9c2e61aef13f5a39","tid":84594,"uid":5962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:00:19.000Z","msg":"我都食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332e68c5b8b5916734597b73402c1cd919d67c74","tid":84594,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"我細個都食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n依家惠康有一盒盒賣<br />\n但隻味道唔似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6da32b52269896589728718ebcef82053b992d","tid":84594,"uid":30208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揾唔揾到圖呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有我記得雀巢出過黑牛， 姐係面頭係可樂味既冰， 入面係朱古力雪糕， 又係揾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cd2a03eb24e24c29ada1ad5a2aecf7cb0637f4","tid":84594,"uid":30208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我細個都食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal